# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:13
translate portuguese jamie14a_b6dcf387:

    # "As I'm leaving for school, somebody calls my name."
    "Quando estou a sair para a escola, alguém chama o meu nome."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:14
translate portuguese jamie14a_b5d0fc44:

    # "Voice" "Hey, [pcname]!"
    "Voice" "Ei, [pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:17
translate portuguese jamie14a_42b89db9:

    # "Jamie's dad is waving me down and walking towards me."
    "O pai do Jamie está a acenar-me e a caminhar na minha direção."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:18
translate portuguese jamie14a_8164aaf1:

    # "Wow, he's looking pretty rough. What the hell does he want?"
    "Uau, ele está com um ar bastante maltratado. Que raio é que ele quer?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:19
translate portuguese jamie14a_cded88c7:

    # "I almost don't even stop. I don't have anything to say to this guy. I want to just keep going to my car and leave."
    "Quase nem paro. Não tenho nada a dizer a este tipo. Só quero seguir em frente até ao meu carro e ir-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:20
translate portuguese jamie14a_aead936c:

    # "But something in his expression and his voice slows me down."
    "Mas algo na sua expressão e na sua voz faz-me abrandar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:23
translate portuguese jamie14a_bea7ca65:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname], can we talk for a minute?"
    jd "Ei, [pcname], podemos conversar um minuto?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:24
translate portuguese jamie14a_810a98a2:

    # pc "What do you want?"
    pc "O que queres?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:25
translate portuguese jamie14a_e6116fb2:

    # jd "I want to... apologize."
    jd "Quero... pedir desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:26
translate portuguese jamie14a_65abe2d1:

    # jd "I messed up."
    jd "Eu estraguei tudo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamie14a_e9e8048e:

    # jd "I don't like you very much. I'm sure you know that."
    jd "Não gosto muito de ti. Tenho a certeza de que sabes disso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamie14a_f70317e8:

    # jd "You broke her heart. I saw how much it hurt her."
    jd "Partiste-lhe o coração. Vi o quanto isso a magoou."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamie14a_62f4e049:

    # jd "She stopped going out with her friends. Stopped trusting people."
    jd "Ela deixou de sair com os amigos. Deixou de confiar nas pessoas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:32
translate portuguese jamie14a_3e24a9b7:

    # jd "And I hated you for that. For hurting my little girl."
    jd "E eu odiei-te por isso. Por magoares a minha menina."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:33
translate portuguese jamie14a_3ef77f3d:

    # jd "When she accepted you back so easily, I didn't understand, and I felt like I needed to protect her from you."
    jd "Quando ela te aceitou de volta tão facilmente, eu não compreendi e senti que precisava de a proteger de ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:36
translate portuguese jamie14a_4c6162ef:

    # jd "But now she's been hurt again and this time it wasn't you that did it."
    jd "Mas agora ela foi magoada outra vez e, desta vez, não foste tu que o fizeste."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:37
translate portuguese jamie14a_154a6154:

    # jd "It was me."
    jd "Fui eu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:38
translate portuguese jamie14a_da05beb6:

    # jd "She really loves you, [pcname]."
    jd "Ela ama-te mesmo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:39
translate portuguese jamie14a_b624fa00:

    # jd "And she's going to resent me forever if I stand in the way of that."
    jd "E vai guardar rancor de mim para sempre se eu me intrometer nisso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:40
translate portuguese jamie14a_ab239c58:

    # pc "So you're saying that I can date Jamie again?"
    pc "Então estás a dizer que posso namorar com a Jamie outra vez?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:43
translate portuguese jamie14a_7ffe4964:

    # jd "I'm saying that I'm going to step aside and let her do what she wants."
    jd "Estou a dizer que vou afastar-me e deixá-la fazer o que quiser."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:44
translate portuguese jamie14a_47573d93:

    # jd "And I'm going to do my best to get along with you."
    jd "E vou dar o meu melhor para me dar bem contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:45
translate portuguese jamie14a_07df80d6:

    # jd "And I hope that you'll accept my apology for getting too protective and overbearing."
    jd "E espero que aceites o meu pedido de desculpas por ter sido demasiado protetor e autoritário."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:46
translate portuguese jamie14a_a1317b53:

    # jd "I just can't stand seeing her sad."
    jd "Simplesmente não suporto vê-la triste."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamie14a_359770ca:

    # jd "So, I'd like to have you over for dinner tonight, if you're not busy."
    jd "Por isso, gostaria de te convidar para jantar esta noite, se não estiveres ocupado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:50
translate portuguese jamie14a_ec06b19e:

    # jd "To show Jamie that I'm okay with you two."
    jd "Para mostrar à Jamie que não tenho problemas com vocês os dois."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:51
translate portuguese jamie14a_bd436701:

    # jd "And to try to repair this whole situation."
    jd "E para tentar reparar toda esta situação."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:52
translate portuguese jamie14a_19e76fb9:

    # jd "If that's okay with you?"
    jd "Se estiveres de acordo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:53
translate portuguese jamie14a_35da6d22:

    # pc "Sure, I think I can do that."
    pc "Claro, acho que posso fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:54
translate portuguese jamie14a_aec7f7b0:

    # jd "Will you shake my hand and put all this behind us?"
    jd "Dá-me um aperto de mão e vamos esquecer tudo isto?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:57
translate portuguese jamie14a_a17b9866:

    # pc "Yeah, I think that's a good idea."
    pc "Sim, acho que é uma boa ideia."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamie14a_501230c4:

    # jd "Good. I'm sorry again."
    jd "Ótimo. Peço desculpa mais uma vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:59
translate portuguese jamie14a_5487b9f8:

    # jd "I can see you're not the same as you were back then."
    jd "Vejo que já não és o mesmo que eras naquela altura."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:60
translate portuguese jamie14a_3e716201:

    # jd "I've seen how much happier Jamie has been since you've come back to Skyhill."
    jd "Tenho visto como a Jamie tem estado mais feliz desde que voltaste para Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamie14a_bb7d1c41:

    # jd "I just want her to be happy."
    jd "Só quero que ela seja feliz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamie14a_78ca39f6:

    # pc "I'll do my best to keep making her happy. I promise."
    pc "Vou dar o meu melhor para continuar a fazê-la feliz. Prometo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:65
translate portuguese jamie14a_c390597e:

    # jd "Alright, [pcname]. Well I'll see you later tonight."
    jd "Tudo bem, [pcname]. Bem, vejo-te mais tarde esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:66
translate portuguese jamie14a_bf178f5a:

    # jd "How do you like your steaks?"
    jd "Como gostas dos teus bifes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:67
translate portuguese jamie14a_2e9a5edb:

    # pc "Medium rare."
    pc "Mal passado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamie14a_778e6fc8:

    # jd "Good answer. See, I like you better already."
    jd "Boa resposta. Vês, já gosto mais de ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:69
translate portuguese jamie14a_4a59320d:

    # pc "Okay, see you later."
    pc "Ok, até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:72
translate portuguese jamie14a_0ced9731:

    # "After Jamie's dad leaves, I get in the car and head to school."
    "Depois de o pai da Jamie sair, entro no carro e dirijo-me para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamie14a_1503cf89:

    # "Guess I'm going to be having dinner with them tonight."
    "Acho que vou jantar com eles esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:74
translate portuguese jamie14a_6b9b4f27:

    # "I hope it's not too awkward!"
    "Espero que não seja muito estranho!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:76
translate portuguese jamie14a_20fd986c:

    # "Later that evening..."
    "Mais tarde nessa noite..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:86
translate portuguese jamie14_e1943713:

    # "I go home and get dressed, putting on something a little nicer than my work clothes, before walking over to Jamie's house to have dinner with her and her dad."
    "Vou para casa e visto-me, colocando algo um pouco mais elegante do que a minha roupa de trabalho, antes de ir até à casa da Jamie para jantar com ela e o pai."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:89
translate portuguese jamie14_00286863:

    # "Before I even knock, Jamie's dad opens the door and greets me."
    "Antes mesmo de bater à porta, o pai da Jamie abre a porta e cumprimenta-me."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:90
translate portuguese jamie14_05eb9994:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname]. Glad you came."
    jd "Olá, [pcname]. Ainda bem que vieste."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:91
translate portuguese jamie14_fc7fda3f:

    # jd "I wasn't sure you would. I know this is going to be a little awkward for everybody."
    jd "Não tinha a certeza se virias. Sei que isto vai ser um pouco estranho para todos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamie14_87d64340:

    # pc "I think it'll be okay."
    pc "Acho que vai correr tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamie14_f9d3ac60:

    # jd "Good. I hope so. Come on in, I just put the steaks on the grill."
    jd "Ótimo. Espero que sim. Entra, acabei de colocar os bifes na grelha."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:96
translate portuguese jamie14_baa894d7:

    # pc "Where's Jamie?"
    pc "Onde está a Jamie?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:97
translate portuguese jamie14_a4f2a7fd:

    # jd "She's still up in her room. She's barely left since I made her break up with you."
    jd "Ainda está no quarto dela. Mal saiu de lá desde que a obriguei a terminar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:98
translate portuguese jamie14_f3737b26:

    # jd "I'm going to call her down for dinner when it's ready and let you surprise her."
    jd "Vou chamá-la para jantar quando estiver pronto e deixar que a surpreendas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:101
translate portuguese jamie14_473a3bfb:

    # jd "I think it'll make her happy to see us getting along."
    jd "Acho que ela vai ficar feliz por ver que nos damos bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:102
translate portuguese jamie14_217a60e1:

    # pc "I hope so. I'm looking forward to seeing her."
    pc "Espero que sim. Estou ansioso por vê-la."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:103
translate portuguese jamie14_f8b1bf29:

    # pc "I've been missing her the last week."
    pc "Tenho sentido a falta dela esta última semana."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:104
translate portuguese jamie14_b320763c:

    # jd "Yeah. I know she missed you too. I'm sorry again."
    jd "Sim. Sei que ela também sentiu a tua falta. Peço desculpa mais uma vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:105
translate portuguese jamie14_d68d94af:

    # pc "It's alright. I know you were just trying to protect your daughter."
    pc "Não faz mal. Sei que só estavas a tentar proteger a tua filha."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:106
translate portuguese jamie14_9810dcb5:

    # pc "I'm glad she has a dad who loves her so much. I know she loves you very much too."
    pc "Fico contente por ela ter um pai que a ama tanto. Sei que ela também te ama muito."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:109
translate portuguese jamie14_dde4aef6:

    # jd "Thanks, [pcname]. That makes me really glad to hear."
    jd "Obrigado, [pcname]. Fico muito contente por ouvir isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:110
translate portuguese jamie14_884f0447:

    # jd "I hope she'll forgive me for all of this."
    jd "Espero que ela me perdoe por tudo isto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:111
translate portuguese jamie14_961e07b1:

    # pc "I know she will."
    pc "Sei que vai perdoar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:112
translate portuguese jamie14_8a978913:

    # jd "My name is Richard, by the way. Rich to friends. I don't know if I've ever really introduced myself."
    jd "A propósito, chamo-me Richard. Rich para os amigos. Não sei se alguma vez me apresentei a sério."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:116
translate portuguese jamie14_4c30d37e:

    # jd "Of course, I hadn't talked to you since you were a punk kid, playing Donkey Kong and sneaking feels in my daughter's bedroom."
    jd "Claro, não falava contigo desde que eras um miúdo rebelde, a jogar Donkey Kong e a espreitar o quarto da minha filha."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:117
translate portuguese jamie14_078bc847:

    # pc "Oh we never did that."
    pc "Oh, nunca fizemos isso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:118
translate portuguese jamie14_acfa9a92:

    # jd "Sure you didn't! And she was just sleeping over at your house last week because your bed is more comfortable."
    jd "Claro que não! E ela só dormiu em tua casa na semana passada porque a tua cama é mais confortável."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:119
translate portuguese jamie14_e7874c6c:

    # pc "That's right."
    pc "É verdade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:120
translate portuguese jamie14_f9b86ca6:

    # "He laughs and I find myself laughing with him. He's not so bad when he doesn't seem to want to kill me."
    "Ele ri-se e dou por mim a rir com ele. Ele não é assim tão mau quando não parece querer matar-me."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:125
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:126
translate portuguese jamie14_3b4e87c7:

    # gnd "Uh...What the heck is going on here?"
    gnd "Uh... O que raio se passa aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:127
translate portuguese jamie14_7574532d:

    # jd "Oh, hey honey. I was about to go upstairs and get you. Dinner's ready."
    jd "Oh, olá, querida. Estava prestes a subir para te ir buscar. O jantar está pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:128
translate portuguese jamie14_23866c5e:

    # gnd "I am very confused right now. Why is [pcname] here?"
    gnd "Estou muito confusa neste momento. Porque é que o [pcname] está aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:131
translate portuguese jamie14_e2bc8a1e:

    # jd "Because I made a mistake."
    jd "Porque cometi um erro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:132
translate portuguese jamie14_0ed25bb5:

    # jd "In trying to protect you from getting your heart broken again..."
    jd "Ao tentar proteger-te de teres o coração partido outra vez..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:133
translate portuguese jamie14_1d42c416:

    # jd "... I ended up breaking it myself."
    jd "... acabei por ser eu a parti-lo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:134
translate portuguese jamie14_b2095d7e:

    # jd "I'm sorry honey."
    jd "Desculpa, querida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:135
translate portuguese jamie14_f3239e98:

    # jd "I'm okay with you dating [pcname]. I'm okay with you doing whatever makes you happy."
    jd "Não me importo que namores com o [pcname]. Não me importo que faças o que te fizer feliz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:136
translate portuguese jamie14_bb351aa3:

    # gnd "Really, Daddy?"
    gnd "A sério, papá?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:137
translate portuguese jamie14_ca7717c2:

    # jd "Really really."
    jd "A sério mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:140
translate portuguese jamie14_4e39c56f:

    # gnd "Thank you, Daddy."
    gnd "Obrigada, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:141
translate portuguese jamie14_04061eae:

    # jd "I love you, honey. I hope you know that."
    jd "Amo-te, querida. Espero que saibas disso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:142
translate portuguese jamie14_63418466:

    # gnd "I love you too, Daddy."
    gnd "Também te amo, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:143
translate portuguese jamie14_0b8d1eb2:

    # jd "I'll take the steaks inside and get the table set. I know you two need to talk."
    jd "Vou levar os bifes para dentro e pôr a mesa. Sei que vocês os dois precisam de conversar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:146
translate portuguese jamie14_69e44ecf:

    # "He carries the food inside and shuts the back door as Jamie walks slowly to me."
    "Ele leva a comida para dentro e fecha a porta das traseiras enquanto a Jamie caminha lentamente na minha direção."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:148
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:149
translate portuguese jamie14_24b3ee56:

    # gnd "I'm sorry that I cut things off like I did."
    gnd "Desculpa ter cortado as pontas assim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:150
translate portuguese jamie14_4addc5b6:

    # gnd "I didn't know what to do."
    gnd "Não sabia o que fazer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:151
translate portuguese jamie14_607ff19c:

    # gnd "I've been crying about it all week."
    gnd "Tenho chorado por causa disso a semana toda."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:153
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:154
translate portuguese jamie14_83f69a35:

    # gnd "Are we okay?"
    gnd "Estamos bem?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:155
translate portuguese jamie14_2e8693f0:

    # pc "Yeah, baby. We're okay."
    pc "Sim, querida. Estamos bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:156
translate portuguese jamie14_d481f95f:

    # pc "Come here."
    pc "Vem cá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:159
translate portuguese jamie14_e043500c:

    # gnd "I missed you so much."
    gnd "Tive tantas saudades tuas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:160
translate portuguese jamie14_4295bf3d:

    # pc "I missed you too."
    pc "Também tive saudades tuas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:161
translate portuguese jamie14_c2110f18:

    # "We kiss like that for a long time. She clings to me like she never wants to let go."
    "Beijamo-nos assim durante muito tempo. Ela agarra-se a mim como se nunca quisesse largar-me."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:164
translate portuguese jamie14_d87fd08d:

    # "Then the back door opens and Rich peeks out."
    "Então a porta das traseiras abre-se e o Rich espreita."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:165
translate portuguese jamie14_774c15a1:

    # jd "Oh, um... sorry. Honey, where is the A1?"
    jd "Oh, hum... desculpa. Querida, onde está o A1?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:166
translate portuguese jamie14_8d809a41:

    # "Jamie doesn't break off the kiss to answer, her lips never leaving mine."
    "A Jamie não interrompe o beijo para responder, os lábios dela nunca se afastam dos meus."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:167
translate portuguese jamie14_50d35669:

    # gnd "Bottom shelf of the refrigerator door."
    gnd "Na prateleira de baixo da porta do frigorífico."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:168
translate portuguese jamie14_13f55642:

    # jd "Okay, thanks honey."
    jd "Está bem, obrigado, querida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:169
translate portuguese jamie14_d6a09f10:

    # jd "Um... everything's on the table, if you're ready to eat."
    jd "Hum... está tudo na mesa, se estiverem prontos para comer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:170
translate portuguese jamie14_fc544f46:

    # gnd "Okay, Daddy. We'll be in in just a minute."
    gnd "Está bem, papá. Já vamos lá num minuto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:171
translate portuguese jamie14_232ae60e:

    # jd "Okay."
    jd "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:172
translate portuguese jamie14_103466ed:

    # jd "Um... no rush."
    jd "Hum... não há pressa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:173
translate portuguese jamie14_f05f4276:

    # "He closes the door and goes back inside."
    "Ele fecha a porta e volta para dentro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:176
translate portuguese jamie14_22af107a:

    # gnd "You're right, you know. I should have just stood up and told him what was going on a long time ago."
    gnd "Tens razão, sabes. Devia ter-me levantado e dito-lhe o que se passava há muito tempo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:177
translate portuguese jamie14_16efaa2c:

    # pc "It all worked out in the end."
    pc "No final, tudo se resolveu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:178
translate portuguese jamie14_01c5d588:

    # gnd "Yeah, but... what if it hadn't."
    gnd "Sim, mas... e se não se tivesse resolvido?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:179
translate portuguese jamie14_e8c450c3:

    # gnd "I really need to work on that. Standing up for myself."
    gnd "Preciso mesmo de trabalhar nisso. Defender-me."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:180
translate portuguese jamie14_0821365b:

    # gnd "And I will."
    gnd "E vou fazê-lo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:182
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:183
translate portuguese jamie14_58ddd8ce:

    # gnd "I'm making a promise. If I want something, I'm going to fight for it."
    gnd "Estou a fazer uma promessa. Se quiser alguma coisa, vou lutar por ela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:185
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:186
translate portuguese jamie14_e5bd6c1c:

    # gnd "I'm not going to let it slip away again, just because I might make somebody upset."
    gnd "Não vou deixar que me escape outra vez, só porque posso chatear alguém."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:187
translate portuguese jamie14_24f5981e:

    # pc "I like that. Your happiness is very important."
    pc "Gosto disso. A tua felicidade é muito importante."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:190
translate portuguese jamie14_1075fe75:

    # gnd "Well, I'm very happy right now."
    gnd "Bem, estou muito feliz neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:191
translate portuguese jamie14_cee162e3:

    # gnd "Although if I knew you were coming, I would have dressed up a little. Maybe brushed my hair."
    gnd "Embora, se soubesse que ias vir, me tivesse arranjado um pouco. Talvez escovado o cabelo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:192
translate portuguese jamie14_709e8dfa:

    # pc "You're gorgeous. Don't worry about that. I'm just glad to be here with you."
    pc "Estás linda. Não te preocupes com isso. Estou apenas feliz por estar aqui contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:193
translate portuguese jamie14_dfd62f7e:

    # gnd "You're so amazing."
    gnd "És tão incrível."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:194
translate portuguese jamie14_c77df519:

    # gnd "Let's go eat."
    gnd "Vamos comer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:198
translate portuguese jamie14_1720c2ef:

    # "We go inside and sit with her dad and have dinner."
    "Entramos, sentamo-nos com o pai dela e jantamos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:199
translate portuguese jamie14_5d82c2b8:

    # "It's not as awkward as I was expecting it to be. Once he gets talking, Rich is pretty funny actually."
    "Não é tão estranho como eu esperava que fosse. Assim que começa a falar, o Rich é bastante engraçado, na verdade."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:200
translate portuguese jamie14_9c723875:

    # "He talks about his work and asks about my school and work."
    "Ele fala sobre o seu trabalho e pergunta sobre a minha escola e o meu trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:201
translate portuguese jamie14_bc6f8d22:

    # "He seems genuinely interested in me and over the course of the meal I can feel him warming up to me a bit."
    "Ele parece genuinamente interessado em mim e, ao longo da refeição, consigo sentir que ele está a ficar um pouco mais à vontade comigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:204
translate portuguese jamie14_ea50946f:

    # jd "I was sorry to hear about your dad. Still no word on what happened to him?"
    jd "Lamentei saber do teu pai. Ainda não se sabe o que lhe aconteceu?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:205
translate portuguese jamie14_7fbf1a0e:

    # pc "No, not yet."
    pc "Não, ainda não."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:206
translate portuguese jamie14_487d47b7:

    # jd "It's really strange."
    jd "É mesmo estranho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:207
translate portuguese jamie14_ede84000:

    # jd "We used to talk through the fence pretty often, but I hadn't seen him in months before the police got involved."
    jd "Costumávamos conversar através da cerca com bastante frequência, mas já não o via há meses antes de a polícia se envolver."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:208
translate portuguese jamie14_86681f0f:

    # pc "Yeah, he became a bit of a hermit, I guess. Spent all his time in his office in the basement."
    pc "Sim, acho que ele se tornou um pouco recluso. Passava todo o tempo no escritório dele na cave."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:211
translate portuguese jamie14_913c87c9:

    # jd "Well, I hope he turns up."
    jd "Bem, espero que ele apareça."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:212
translate portuguese jamie14_1bbf0a93:

    # jd "Hopefully he just took some time off to himself and he'll come home eventually."
    jd "Espero que tenha apenas tirado algum tempo para si e que acabe por voltar para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:213
translate portuguese jamie14_e82b335f:

    # pc "I hope so."
    pc "Espero que sim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:214
translate portuguese jamie14_4543d9f2:

    # "Sitting here and talking to Jamie's dad just reminds me how much I miss my own father."
    "Sentar-me aqui a conversar com o pai da Jamie só me faz lembrar o quanto sinto falta do meu próprio pai."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:217
translate portuguese jamie14_09aa50f4:

    # "They are pretty similar actually. Hard-working. Funny."
    "Na verdade, eles são bastante parecidos. Trabalhadores. Engraçados."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:218
translate portuguese jamie14_fdfc1ad7:

    # "Both of them have lost their wife too."
    "Ambos perderam a mulher também."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:219
translate portuguese jamie14_c5b26d00:

    # "But while Jamie's dad turned to his family after the death and held them closer, my dad had..."
    "Mas enquanto o pai da Jamie se voltou para a família após a morte e os aproximou mais, o meu pai tinha..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:220
translate portuguese jamie14_1adb6623:

    # "... well, whatever my dad had done, I'm not really sure."
    "... bem, o que quer que o meu pai tenha feito, não tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:223
translate portuguese jamie14_398e8474:

    # "After dinner, Jamie and I sit in her backyard together, looking up at the stars."
    "Depois do jantar, a Jamie e eu sentamo-nos juntos no quintal dela, a olhar para as estrelas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:224
translate portuguese jamie14_c08e5558:

    # gnd "That was really nice."
    gnd "Foi muito bom."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:225
translate portuguese jamie14_66c0b088:

    # pc "Yeah it was."
    pc "Sim, foi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:226
translate portuguese jamie14_73145f9f:

    # gnd "I love that we don't have to hide anymore."
    gnd "Adoro que já não tenhamos de nos esconder."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:227
translate portuguese jamie14_a8284af3:

    # pc "It's not going to ruin the passion?"
    pc "Isso não vai estragar a paixão?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:230
translate portuguese jamie14_64527f8a:

    # gnd "Absolutely not."
    gnd "De forma alguma."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:231
translate portuguese jamie14_37ba49d4:

    # gnd "I don't think Daddy is gonna want us having sex at the house or anything..."
    gnd "Acho que o papá não vai querer que façamos sexo em casa nem nada..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:232
translate portuguese jamie14_86cdae76:

    # gnd "... but I can't wait to spend another night with you."
    gnd "... mas mal posso esperar para passar outra noite contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:233
translate portuguese jamie14_04491fb2:

    # pc "Want to come over tonight?"
    pc "Queres vir cá esta noite?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:236
translate portuguese jamie14_5632c3e4:

    # gnd "Soon, but not tonight."
    gnd "Em breve, mas não esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:237
translate portuguese jamie14_33db0ab9:

    # gnd "I think I need to talk to Daddy some alone, you know?"
    gnd "Acho que preciso de falar com o pai a sós, percebes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:238
translate portuguese jamie14_9d09aa00:

    # gnd "It seems like we're better, but we still have some things we need to work through."
    gnd "Parece que estamos melhor, mas ainda temos algumas coisas que precisamos de resolver."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:239
translate portuguese jamie14_34b44705:

    # pc "I understand."
    pc "Eu compreendo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:242
translate portuguese jamie14_8749741d:

    # gnd "But things are going to be good, I know it."
    gnd "Mas as coisas vão correr bem, eu sei disso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:243
translate portuguese jamie14_677d7bb7:

    # gnd "Thanks for everything, [pcname]."
    gnd "Obrigada por tudo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:244
translate portuguese jamie14_fe2167ed:

    # gnd "I know it probably wasn't easy to make tonight happen, to patch things up with Daddy."
    gnd "Sei que provavelmente não foi fácil fazer com que esta noite acontecesse, para fazer as pazes com o pai."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:245
translate portuguese jamie14_56e12139:

    # gnd "So thank you for doing that. For not holding things against him."
    gnd "Por isso, obrigado por fazeres isso. Por não guardares rancor dele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:248
translate portuguese jamie14_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:249
translate portuguese jamie14_f9831d1e:

    # gnd "I love you, [pcname]."
    gnd "Amo-te, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:250
translate portuguese jamie14_5e3e613a:

    # pc "I love you too, Jamie."
    pc "Também te amo, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:251
translate portuguese jamie14_53a4b911:

    # "We lie there for a while longer, holding each other and enjoying the cool night air."
    "Ficamos ali deitados por mais algum tempo, abraçados e a apreciar o ar fresco da noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:254
translate portuguese jamie14_f4805d30:

    # "Then I tell her and Rich goodbye and go back over to my house, leaving them to work out whatever they need to."
    "Depois, digo adeus a ela e ao Rich e volto para minha casa, deixando-os a resolver o que precisarem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:255
translate portuguese jamie14_acdbbb7b:

    # "It feels like Jamie and I took a big step in our relationship today."
    "Parece que a Jamie e eu demos um grande passo na nossa relação hoje."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:256
translate portuguese jamie14_9d2f13b4:

    # "Things are getting more serious. I promised her dad that I wouldn't hurt her."
    "As coisas estão a ficar mais sérias. Prometi ao pai dela que não a magoaria."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:257
translate portuguese jamie14_ad87ea57:

    # "I hope I can keep that promise."
    "Espero conseguir cumprir essa promessa."

